%20gunned%20down%20in%20a%20single%20incident%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%20region%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFour%20civilians%2C%20including%20a%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%2C%20were%20also%20killed%20in%20terror%20incidents%20in%20the%20valley%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20violence%20is%20subsiding%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20number%20of%20casualties%20suffered%20by%20security%20forces%20in%20Jammu%2C%20which%20was%20declared%20militancy-free%20some%20years%20ago%2C%20has%20nearly%20doubled.%20The%20theatre%20of%20militancy%20has%20seemingly%20shifted%20to%20Jammu%E2%80%99s%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20which%20bounds%20the%20valley%20from%20the%20west%20and%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fembed%3Fmid%3D1i0tKjoDISxQqe7W0lF8l6es3YDXqyEM%26ehbc%3D2E312F%26noprof%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Pir%20Panjal%20conundrum%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20chain%20of%20mountains%20in%20the%20lower%20Himalayas%2C%20extending%20from%20Gulmarg%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20to%20Kishtwar%20in%20the%20south%20from%20where%20it%20stretches%20into%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20comprises%20Poonch%2C%20Rajouri%20and%20Reasi%20districts%20of%20Jammu%20division%20which%20is%20home%20to%20lush%20forests%20and%20some%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20highest%20peaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPir%20Panjal%20has%20reportedly%20turned%20into%20a%20haven%20for%20foreign%20infiltrators%20%E2%80%93%20sneaking%20into%20J%26amp%3BK%20from%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20local%20militants%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20taking%20shelter%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20dense%20forests%20which%20have%20natural%20caves%20shielded%20under%20thick%20vegetation%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20an%20unspecified%20number%20of%20foreigners%2C%20aided%20by%20local%20militants%20and%20some%20civilians%2C%20are%20shuttling%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20which%20separates%20Jammu%20division%20from%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20and%20even%20reportedly%20crossing%20back%20the%20LoC%20into%20Pakistan%20occupied%20J%26amp%3BK%20(PoJ%26amp%3BK)%20after%20carrying%20out%20deadly%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20and%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20shows%20that%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20army%20soldiers%20and%20dozens%20of%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20militant%20attacks%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%20in%20Pir%20Panjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwho-is-uzair-bashir-khan-the-kashmiri-militant-behind-the-deadly-kokernag-attack%5C%22%3EWho%20Was%20Uzair%20Bashir%20Khan%2C%20the%20Kashmiri%20Militant%20Behind%20the%20Deadly%20Kokernag%20Attack%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20fortnight%20alone%2C%20security%20forces%20and%20militants%20were%20caught%20in%20at%20least%20six%20face-offs%20across%20the%20union%20territory%2C%20including%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20the%20capital%2C%20where%20an%20unidentified%20militant%20opened%20fire%20on%20a%20truck%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Paramilitary%20Forces%20(CRPF)%20in%20Khanyar%20locality%20on%20September%2018%20but%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20cause%20any%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFour%20of%20these%20face-offs%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20or%20its%20adjoining%20areas.%20Some%20of%20these%20face-offs%20have%20turned%20deadly%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20six%20security%20personnel%2C%20including%20three%20officers%2C%20in%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20anti-militancy%20operation%20in%20Kokernag.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20seven%20militants%20were%20also%20gunned%20down%20over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20of%20which%20six%20militants%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EInfiltration%20woes%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20activity%20of%20militants%20in%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20has%20prompted%20officials%20to%20relook%20at%20the%20winter%20strategy%20for%20containing%20militancy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Officials%20and%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2F5-incidents-in-10-days-cross-border-spike-turns-gaze-to-winter-strategy-8943188%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20increasing%20violence%20points%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20fresh%20infiltration%20along%20the%20LoC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20uptick%20in%20violence%20is%20consistent%20with%20the%20past%20trends%20as%20foreign%20militants%20try%20to%20sneak%20across%20the%20LoC%20before%20the%20winter%20snow%20on%20high%20mountain%20passes%20makes%20J%26amp%3BK%20inaccessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20two%20years%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20has%20accused%20Islamabad%20of%20violating%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fafter-february-ceasefire-agreement-first-pakistani-sporting-team-arrives-in-india%5C%22%3E2011%20Ceasefire%20Agreement%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20vowed%20to%20uphold%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20by%20providing%20%E2%80%9Cfire%20support%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20group%20of%20infiltrators%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20were%20later%20gunned%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20insurgency-related%20violence%20has%20quieted%2C%20the%20number%20of%20active%20militants%20breached%20the%20double-digit%20mark%20achieved%20last%20year%20to%20reach%20107%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20including%2071%20foreign%20militants.%20This%20has%20raised%20red-flags%20in%20the%20security%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20national%20English%20daily%20reported%20that%20only%2081%20militants%20were%20active%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20the%20month%20of%20August.%20The%20report%20excludes%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%98hybrid%E2%80%99%20militants%2C%20a%20new%20term%20used%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20to%20describe%20the%20militants%20who%20have%20not%20been%20identified%20due%20to%20their%20undercover%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUptick%20in%20militancy%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20and%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20there%20are%2015%20active%20militants%20in%20Jammu%20region%20with%20two%20of%20them%20believed%20to%20be%20foreigners.%20But%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20militants%20are%20shifting%20bases%20between%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20indicates%20that%20the%20number%20could%20be%20on%20the%20higher%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2070%25%20militants%20active%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20affiliated%20with%20Pakistan-based%20Jaish-e-Mohammad%20and%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20outfits%20which%2C%20officials%20believe%2C%20operate%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Peoples%20Anti-Fascist%20Force%20and%20The%20Resistance%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20over%20600%20overground%20workers%20of%20militants%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20anti-terror%20laws%20with%20most%20of%20them%20incarcerated%20in%20jails%20outside%20the%20union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20significant%20development%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Jammu%20police%20was%20sent%20on%20a%20central%20deputation%20earlier%20this%20week%20while%20the%20head%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Paramilitary%20Forces%E2%80%99%20Kashmir%20operations%20was%20prematurely%20repatriated%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMukesh%20Singh%2C%20a%201996%20IPS%20officer%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20Jammu%2C%20(ADGP)%20since%202019%2C%20has%20been%20sent%20on%20a%20central%20deputation%20with%20the%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20(ITBP)%20for%20five%20years%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695378296000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F04170315%2F15693039226_bc366e1bf3_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjk-uptick-in-violence-ahead-of-winter-possibility-of-fresh-infiltration-along-the-loc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officials%20said%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20violence%20is%20consistent%20with%20past%20trends%20as%20foreign%20militants%20try%20to%20sneak%20across%20the%20LoC%20before%20the%20winter%20snow%20on%20high%20mountain%20passes%20makes%20J%26amp%3BK%20inaccessible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjk-uptick-in-violence-ahead-of-winter-possibility-of-fresh-infiltration-along-the-loc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20Is%20In%20Fine%20Fettle%20In%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20after%20the%20%3Cem%3EThugs%20of%20Hindostan%3C%2Fem%3E%20debacle%2C%20the%20team%20of%20producer%20Aditya%20Chopra%20and%20writer-director%20Vijay%20Krishna%20Acharya%20are%20back%20with%20a%20rambunctious%20dramedy%20that%2C%20notwithstanding%20a%20clutch%20of%20trivial%20contrivances%2C%20makes%20amends%20of%20sorts.%20It%20delivers%20a%20welcome%20%26quot%3Bunity%20in%20diversity%26quot%3B%20message%20in%20an%20entertaining%2C%20unpretentious%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20advocacy%20of%20pluralism%20and%20inclusivity%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20facile%20the%20methods%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Indian%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%20employs%20are%2C%20makes%20perfect%20sense%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20current%20socio-political%20climate%20in%20which%20othering%20is%20one%20of%20our%20favourite%20collective%20pastimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Indian%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20celebrates%20the%20beauty%20of%20a%20dynamic%20nation's%20time-tested%20syncretism%2C%20traverses%20down%20a%20somewhat%20laborious%20path%20in%20reaching%20the%20conclusion%20that%20a%20mahaul%20(environment)%20and%20a%20mohalla%20(neighbourhood)%20that%20lack%20variety%20and%20try%20to%20impose%20a%20single%20colour%20and%20credo%20on%20everybody%20should%20be%20anathema%20to%20all%20right-thinking%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20its%20missteps%2C%20which%20are%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20tics%20that%20popular%20Hindi%20cinema%20cannot%20usually%20do%20without%2C%20the%20film%20deserves%20to%20be%20commended%20for%20talking%20up%20the%20need%20for%20harmony%20at%20a%20time%20when%20segments%20of%20Bollywood%20are%20falling%20over%20each%20other%20to%20profit%20from%20narratives%20that%20are%20dipped%20in%20venom%20and%20vitriol.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Indian%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20about%20a%20successful%20bhajan%20singer%20whose%20life%20is%20turned%20upside%20down%20when%20a%20letter%20that%20arrives%20like%20a%20bolt%20from%20the%20blue%20claims%20that%20his%20religious%20identity%20is%20different%20from%20that%20of%20his%20father%2C%20a%20Hindu%20priest%20revered%20by%20one%20and%20all%20in%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Balrampur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVed%20Vyas%20Tripathi%2C%20alias%20Billu%2C%20is%20%26quot%3BBhajan%20Kumar%26quot%3B%20(Vicky%20Kaushal)%2C%20the%20undisputed%20king%20of%20the%20devotional%20songs%20circuit.%20He%20has%20a%20fan%20following%20to%20die%20for.%20And%20his%20father%20is%20the%20go-to%20man%20for%20every%20major%20religious%20ceremony%20in%20town%2C%20one%20of%20which%20presents%20Billu%2C%20as%20a%20schoolboy%2C%20to%20show%20the%20world%20his%20singing%20skills.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBillu%20believes%20that%20life%20is%20like%20is%20a%20game%20of%20snakes%20and%20ladders%20and%20his%20family%20members%20are%20the%20poisonous%20ones%20snapping%20at%20his%20heels.%20His%20fear%20comes%20true%20when%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20he%20isn't%20a%20Hindu%20although%20he%20was%20raised%20as%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20that%20the%20discovery%20of%20his%20origins%20sparks%20-%20his%20father%20Siyaram%20Tripathi%20(Kumud%20Mishra)%20is%20away%20on%20his%20annual%20pilgrimage%20when%20a%20letter%20from%20a%20dead%20man%20divulges%20the%20truth%20of%20his%20birth%20-%20drives%20a%20wedge%20between%20Billu%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family.%20He%20is%20all%20but%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20flock%20and%20a%20vicious%20social%20media%20campaign%20threatens%20to%20end%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20big%20wedding%20is%20up%20ahead%20and%20Billu's%20uncle%2C%20Balak%20Ram%20Tripathi%20(Manoj%20Pahwa)%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20family%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20his%20elder%20brother%2C%20decides%20to%20keep%20the%20bhajan%20singer%20out%20of%20the%20fold%20for%20fear%20of%20losing%20the%20lucrative%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Billu%20has%20no%20clue%20why%20everybody%20thinks%20that%20he%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20person%20he%20was%2C%20his%20religion%20gives%20those%20that%20want%20to%20see%20his%20family%20come%20to%20grief%20a%20stick%20to%20beat%20him%20with.%20He%20resolves%20to%20take%20the%20blows%20on%20the%20chin%20until%20it%20becomes%20absolutely%20clear%20that%20he%20has%20no%20option%20but%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FjxRgnlvep94%3Fsi%3DCe7ZSDz4m6sSjoAz%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tone%20of%20the%20112-minute%20film's%20opening%20moments%20belies%20the%20serious%20turn%20that%20it%20takes%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20halfway%20mark.%20Billu%2C%20in%20his%20own%20voice%2C%20narrates%20his%20back%20story%20and%20introduces%20the%20audience%20to%20his%20family%20-%20his%20father%2C%20his%20uncle%2C%20his%20bua%20(Alka%20Amin)%2C%20his%20chachi%20(Sadiya%20Siddiqui)%20and%20his%20twin%20sister%20Gunja%20(Srishti%20Dixit).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20throws%20in%20a%20quick%20reference%20to%20a%20rival%20Balrampur%20priest%20(Yashpal%20Sharma)%20and%20his%20son%20(Aasif%20Khan)%2C%20who%20are%20bent%20upon%20countering%20the%20goodwill%20that%20Billu's%20sagacious%20father%20enjoys%20in%20the%20community.%20The%20stage%20is%20thus%20set%20for%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20two%20families%20for%20the%20religious%20rituals%20that%20are%20up%20for%20grabs%20-%20a%20battle%20in%20which%20the%20Tripathis%20always%20have%20their%20noses%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20early%20scene%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Indian%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%20appears%20to%20be%20heading%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction.%20Billu%20and%20two%20pals%20enter%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20locality%20to%20stop%20a%20boy%20called%20Abdul%20from%20a%20romantic%20rendezvous.%20The%20trio%20calls%20themselves%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-Majnu%20squad%26quot%3B.%20The%20terms%20that%20they%20use%20before%20they%20go%20about%20scaring%20off%20Abdul%20-%20no%20man's%20land%2C%20surgical%20strike%2C%20et%20all%20-%20suggest%20a%20problematic%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20exactly%20the%20screenwriter%20is%20driving%20at%20becomes%20clear%20when%20in%20the%20very%20next%20sequence%2C%20Billu%20and%20his%20friends%20receive%20instant%20comeuppance.%20A%20feisty%20young%20girl%20from%20Jalandhar%2C%20Jasmine%20(Manushi%20Chhillar)%2C%20who%2C%20it%20is%20soon%20revealed%2C%20is%20also%20a%20crooner%20and%20dancer%2C%20puts%20them%20in%20their%20place.%20She%20schools%20them%20on%20respecting%20those%20that%20are%20different%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESufficiently%20chastised%20by%20the%20belligerent%20Jasmine%2C%20Billu%20and%20his%20friends%20visit%20Abdul's%20home%20to%20apologise%20to%20him.%20There%20they%20learn%20that%20Abdul's%20brother%20Pintu%20is%20the%20actor%20who%20plays%20Kumbhakarna%20in%20Balrampur's%20Ramlila.%20Their%20mother%20refuses%20to%20let%20Billu%20leave%20without%20making%20tea%20for%20the%20boys.%20The%20encounter%20helps%20the%20protagonist%20see%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20thrust%20of%20what%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Indian%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20trying%20to%20tell%20an%20audience%20that%20is%20increasingly%20told%20to%20believe%20the%20exact%20opposite.%20In%20the%20garish%2C%20high-pitched%2C%20seemingly%20'uncool'%20world%20that%20Billu%20and%20his%20devout%20Hindu%20family%20inhabit%2C%20cinematographer%20Ayananka%20Bose%20revels%20in%20heightening%20the%20loud%20colours%20that%20dominate%20the%20elaborate%20and%20busy%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20over-wrought%20visuals%20sit%20well%20with%20the%20discourse%20that%20runs%20through%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Indian%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20sees%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20in%20fine%20fettle.%20The%20support%20that%20his%20energetic%20performance%20receives%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cast%20-%20Kumud%20Mishra%20and%20Manoj%20Pahwa%20in%20particular%20-%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20script%20does%20not%2C%20however%2C%20do%20justice%20to%20the%20hero's%20romantic%20interest%20-%20the%20outspoken%20and%20assertive%20Jasmine%2C%20played%20by%20Manushi%20Chhillar.%20The%20character%2C%20especially%20because%20of%20the%20ideas%20that%20she%20espouses%2C%20deserved%20more%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Indian%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20have%20been%20a%20film%20of%20far%20greater%20acuity%2C%20but%20the%20broadsides%20that%20it%20aims%20against%20narrow-mindedness%20through%20the%20story%20of%20a%20family%20as%20a%20microcosm%20of%20a%20soci