gged%20me%20into%20this%20unfortunate%20incident%20where%20two%20MPs%20were%20using%20unparliamentary%20language%20against%20each%20other%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Vardhan%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20couldn't%20hear%20clearly%20what%20was%20being%20said%20due%20to%20chaos%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20sad%20and%20humiliated%20that%20some%20people%20with%20vested%20interest%20have%20dragged%20my%20name%20into%20this.%20While%20I%20was%20no%20doubt%20witness%20to%20the%20jugglery%20of%20words%20being%20thrown%20at%20each%20other%20(which%20in%20fact%20the%20entire%20House%20was)%2C%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20in%20the%20chaos%20that%20existed%2C%20I%20could%20not%20clearly%20hear%20what%20was%20being%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20Union%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDanish%20Ali%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%2C%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Speaker%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bheartbreaking%26quot%3B%20incident%20for%20him%20as%20a%20minority%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20told%20reporters%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20an%20elected%20MP%20had%20to%20face%20such%20threats%20and%20%26quot%3Bhate%20speech%26quot%3B%20on%20record%20and%20that%20he%20couldn't%20sleep%20all%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpposition%20Congress%20said%20Rajnath%20Singh's%20apology%20was%20not%20enough%20and%20that%20Mr%20Bidhuri%20should%20be%20suspended%20or%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20absolute%20shame.%20Rajnath%20Singh's%20apology%20is%20not%20acceptable%20and%20half-hearted.%20This%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20parliament%2C%20this%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20suspension%20and%20Bidhuri%20statement%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20every%20Indian%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20demanding%20%26quot%3Bstrictest%20possible%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20BJP%20leader.%