oga%20district%20was%20killed%20in%20Winnipeg.%20The%20information%20was%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Homicide%20Unit%20of%20Winnipeg%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Manitoba%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20there%20was%20no%20official%20confirmation%20of%20Gill%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20In%20a%20press%20release%20issued%20on%20September%2021%2C%20the%20Homicide%20Unit%20Winnipeg%20confirmed%20the%20crime%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Homicide%20Unit%20has%20now%20identified%20the%20victim%20as%2039-year-old%20Sukhdool%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20and%20notifications%20to%20family%20members%20have%20been%20made.%20The%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20previous%20statement%2C%20the%20Winnipeg%20police%20said%20that%20on%20September%2020%2C%20at%20around%2010%20am%2C%20the%20North%20District%20General%20Patrol%20Officers%2C%20assisted%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Tactical%20Support%20Team%2C%20went%20to%20a%20residence%20in%20the%20200%20block%20of%20Hazelton%20Drive%2C%20where%20they%20located%20the%20deceased%20adult%20victim.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGill%E2%80%99s%20killing%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20ongoing%20standoff%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20and%20claims%20by%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20that%20India%20was%20behind%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Sukha%20Duneke%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESukhdool%20Singh%20Gill%20alias%20Sukha%20Duneke%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20Duneke%20village%20of%20Moga%20district.%20Sukha%E2%80%99s%20name%20had%20figured%20in%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%E2%80%99s%20wanted%20list%2C%20which%20was%20released%20on%20September%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGill%20allegedly%20reached%20Canada%20on%20a%20fake%20passport%20in%202017.%20Before%20fleeing%20to%20Canada%2C%20he%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%2