Url%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Minister%20Cancels%20China%20Asian%20Games%20Visit%20As%20Arunachal%20Players%20Denied%20Visa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Friday%20filed%20a%20formal%20protest%20against%20China's%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20and%20selective%20obstruction%20of%20sportspersons%26quot%3B%20after%20Beijing%20denied%20visas%20and%20accreditation%20to%20athletes%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20has%20also%20cancelled%20his%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20of%20India%20has%20learnt%20Chinese%20authorities%20have%2C%20in%20a%20targeted%20and%20pre-meditated%20manner%2C%20discriminated%20against%20some%20Indian%20sportspersons%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20by%20denying%20them%20accreditation%20and%20entry%20to%20the%2019th%20Asian%20Games%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20line%20with%20our%20long-standing%20and%20consistent%20position%2C%20India%20firmly%20rejects%20differential%20treatment%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20on%20basis%20of%20domicile%20or%20ethnicity.%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20was%2C%20is%20and%20will%20always%20remain%20an%20integral%20and%20inalienable%20part%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagchi%20said%20the%20government%20had%20lodged%20a%20strong%20protest%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Beijing%20over%20China's%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20and%20selective%20obstruction%26quot%3B%20of%20Indian%20athletes.%20He%20said%20the%20government%20had%20noted%20that%20these%20actions%20%26quot%3Bviolate%20both%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Asian%20Games%20and%20rules%20governing%20their%20conduct%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20%26quot%3Breserves%20the%20right%20to%20take%20suitable%20measures%20to%20safeguard%20(its)%20interests%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Bagchi%20added