ks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20injured%20suspects%20were%20both%20shot%20in%20the%20right%20leg%20near%20the%20knee%20and%20were%20identified%20as%20Azad%20and%20Vishwambhar%20Dayal%20Dubey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20successive%20alleged%20%E2%80%98encounter%E2%80%99%20shootings%20in%20two%20different%20police%20station%20areas%20come%20after%20an%20extensive%20operation%20launched%20by%20the%20state%20police%20to%20crack%20the%20case%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20head%20constable%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20August%2030%20and%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2047-year%20woman%20head%20constable%20Sumitra%20Patel%20was%20found%20lying%20unconscious%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20under%20a%20seat%20of%20the%20Saryu%20Express%20while%20she%20was%20travelling%20to%20attend%20duty%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20brutal%20attack%20on%20her%20had%20left%20authorities%20puzzled%20as%20they%20struggled%20to%20trace%20the%20culprits%20or%20a%20motive%20behind%20the%20attack.%20A%20few%20days%20after%20the%20attack%2C%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20Chief%20Justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker%20even%20took%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20cognisance%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20provide%20details%20of%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2016%2C%20the%20UP%20police%20announced%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20anyone%20who%20would%20provide%20information%20about%20the%20culprits.%20On%20September%2022%2C%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Ayodhya%20Raj%20Karan%20Nayyar%20said%20during%20investigation%20that%20the%20victim%20had%20recognised%20one%20of%20the%20suspects%20whose%20photograph%20was%20shown%20to%20her%20by%20the%20UP%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Task%20Force%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20these%20inputs%2C%20the%20district%20police%20and%20the%20STF%20conducted%20a%20raid%20in%20Inayat%20Nagar%20area%20of%20Ayodhya%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused%2C%20said%20Nayyar.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20accused%20fired%20at%20the%20police%20team%20which%20fired%20back%20in%20self-defence.%20Police%20arrested%20two%20accused%20persons%20who%20were%20injured%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nayyar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20said%20that%20a%20third%20suspect%2C%20identified%20as%20Aneesh%20Khan%2C%20had%20escaped%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98encounter%E2%80%99%20site%20while%20firing%20at%20the%20police.%20A%20search%20operation%20was%20launched%20to%20arrest%20him%20and%20he%20was%20soon%20located%20in%20an%20area%20falling%20under%20police%20station%20Pura%20Kalandar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20person%20was%20asked%20to%20surrender%2C%20said%20Nayyar.%20Khan%20allegedly%20fired%20at%20the%20police%20who%20shot%20him%20while%20firing%20in%20self-defence%2C%20according%20to%20Nayyar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Haiderganj%2C%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20district%20hospital%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERatan%20Sharma%2C%20the%20station%20house%20officer%20of%20Pura%20Kalandar%20was%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98encounter%E2%80%99%2C%20said%20police%2C%20but%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20police%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years%20of%20the%20Adityanath%20government%2C%20has%20been%20known%20to%20kill%20those%20accused%20in%20serious%20crimes%20through%20alleged%20encounters.%20In%20March%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fup-police-eliminated-178-in-10-7k-encounters-in-6-yrs-of-yogi-govt-data-101678986724825.html%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20had%20analysed%3C%2Fa%3E%20district-wise%20data%20to%20note%20that%20178%20accused%20were%20killed%20during%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20in%20as%20many%20as%2010%2C713%20encounters%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fup-four-times-more-people-killed-in-police-action-under-adityanath-than-akhilesh-yadav%5C%22%3EUP%3A%20Four%20Times%20More%20People%20Killed%20in%20%E2%80%98Police%20Action%E2%80%99%20Under%20Adityanath%20Than%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20claimed%20that%20the%20two%20suspects%20who%20were%20arrested%20had%20confessed%20to%20attacking%20the%20head%20constable.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20reveal%20the%20alleged%20motive%20behind%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20attack%20on%20the%20constable%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20head%20constable%20is%20recovering%20in%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPosted%20in%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Sultanpur%20district%2C%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2030%20and%2031%20she%20was%20aboard%20the%20Saryu%20Express%20on%20her%20way%20to%20duty%20at%20the%20Hanuman%20Gadi%20Sawan%20Mela%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Due%20to%20some%20reasons%2C%20she%20missed%20her%20stop%20and%20reached%20the%20final%20destination%2C%20Mankapur%20railway%20station%2C%20from%20where%20she%20took%20the%20train%20back%20towards%20Ayodhya.%20However%2C%20between%20these%20two%20stations%2C%20she%20was%20assaulted%20by%20some%20unknown%20person(s)%20with%20sharp%20objects%2C%20leaving%20her%20badly%20injured%2C%20bleeding%20and%20unconscious%20under%20a%20berth%20in%20one%20of%20the%20coaches.%20On%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20complaint%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20Government%20Railway%20Police%2C%20Cantonment%20police%20station%2C%20in%20Ayodhya%20against%20unknown%20persons%20under%20charges%20including%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%20assault%20or%20use%20of%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20disrobe%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20ruled%20out%20sexual%20assault%20as%20the%20medico-legal%20test%20and%20forensic%20investigation%20did%20not%20confirm%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%204%2C%20UP%20DGP%20Vijay%20Kumar%20and%20special%20DG%20law%20and%20order%20Prashant%20Kumar%20both%20said%20the%20case%20would%20be%20solved%20soon%20and%20the%20real%20culprits%20would%20be%20arrested.%20Officer%20Prashant%20Kumar%20along%20with%20principal%20secretary%20(home)%20Sanjay%20Prasad%20visited%20the%20injured%20woman%20constable%20at%20the%20trauma%20centre%20of%20the%20King%20George%E2%80%99s%20Medical%20University%20in%20Lucknow.%20UP%20police%20along%20with%20railway%20officials%20even%20conducted%20a%20scene%20recreation%20exercise%20of%20the%20incident%20on%20September%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%203%2C%20HC%20Chief%20Justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker%20and%20Justice%20Ashutosh%20Srivastava%20took%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20cognisance%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgruesome%20incident%E2%80%9D%20and%20directed%20the%20court%20registry%20to%20register%20the%20matter%20as%20a%20criminal%20public%20interest%20litigation.%20The%20court%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20as%20well%20as%20the%20state.%20The%20case%20was%20brought%20to%20CJ%20Diwaker%E2%80%99s%20attention%20by%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20he%20received%20from%20an%20advocate%20Ram%20Kaushik%20at%20around%203.35%20pm%20on%20Sunday%2C%20September%203%2C%20following%20which%20the%20CJ%20constituted%20a%20bench%20at%208%20pm%20at%20his%20residence%20to%20hear%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20petition%2C%20advocate%20Kaushik%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9CRailway%20Authorities%20have%20completely%20failed%20to%20implement%20the%20various%20safety%20measures%20involving%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20women.%20The%20present%20incident%20clearly%20shows%20the%20utter%20violation%20of%20the%20certain%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20also%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20failed%20in%20discharge%20of%20their%20duties%20and%20responsibilities%20in%20giving%20effect%20to%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20formulated%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20passengers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Diwaker%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20summoned%20the%20investigation%20officer%20of%20the%20case%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20September%204%20with%20the%20case%20diary.%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(GRP)%2C%20Pooja%20Yadav%20appeared%20in%20court%20and%20informed%20the%20judges%20that%20five%20teams%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20circle%20officer%20and%20deputy%20SP%20had%20been%20formed%20to%20solve%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInjuries%20were%20inflicted%20upon%20Sumitra%E2%80%99s%20face%20and%20upper%20body%20parts%20with%20a%20sharp-edged%20weapon%2C%20presumably%20a%20chopper%2C%20said%20Yadav.%20The%20court%20took%20note%20of%20the%20progress%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20said%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20doubt%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20proceeding%20in%20the%20right%20track%20and%20would%20bring%20results%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695369646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F23105411%2F698802-uttar-pradesh-police-pti-file.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-woman-constable-attack-aneesh-khan-shot-dead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20successive%20alleged%20'encounter'%20shootings%20in%20two%20different%20police%20station%20areas%20come%20after%20an%20extensive%20operation%20launched%20by%20the%20state%20police%20to%20crack%20the%20case%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20head%20constable%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20August%2030%20and%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-woman-constable-attack-aneesh-khan-shot-dead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%20BJP%20Can%20Allay%20Doubts%20About%20its%20Commitment%20to%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22104636%2FF6kk7dtXkAEhH2a.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20or%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%2C%20passed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20tests%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20but%20not%20before%20the%20Opposition%20slammed%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20delaying%20its%20implementation%20by%20tying%20the%20legislation%20to%20a%20Census%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20rightly%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20over%2013%20years%2C%20Indian%20women%20have%20waited%20to%20take%20their%20political%20responsibility%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20being%20told%20to%20wait%20for%20some%20more%20years.%20How%20many%20years%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20%E2%80%93%20two%20years%2C%20four%20years%2C%20six%20years%2C%20eight%20years%3F%20Is%20such%20a%20treatment%20towards%20Indian%20women%20appropriate%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20bill%20was%20finalised%20by%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20in%20a%20surprise%20move%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament%2C%20the%20Opposition%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20government%20for%20keeping%20it%20a%20secret.%20They%20questioned%20the%20need%20for%20such%20secrecy%20as%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20bill%20could%20have%20been%20easily%20achieved.%20The%20government%20has%20continued%20with%20its%20non-consultative%20and%20autocratic%20behaviour%20even%20in%20a%20matter%20where%20prior%20discussions%20could%20have%20only%20smoothened%20the%20bill%E2%80%99s%20course%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Opposition%20parties%20alleged%20that%20the%20bill%20was%20another%20%E2%80%9Celection%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20ahead%20of%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20five%20states%2C%20and%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20honest%20intention%20to%20implement%20it.%20Their%20claim%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%202021%20decadal%20Census%2C%20delayed%20by%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20has%20now%20been%20postponed%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20Resultantly%2C%20the%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%2C%20which%20has%20to%20happen%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20Census%20data%2C%20cannot%20be%20carried%20out%20anytime%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20Having%2033%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20constituencies%20reserved%20for%20women%2C%20therefore%2C%20looks%20like%20a%20distant%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20even%20cries%20from%20some%20quarters%20that%20the%20current%20script%20of%20the%20bill%20allows%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20postpone%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20by%20at%20least%2010%20years.%20Many%20observers%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20saw%20the%20move%20as%20a%20ploy%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20get%20leverage%20over%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20has%20been%20consistently%20demanding%20a%20caste%20census%20%E2%80%95%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20thorn%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20cacophony%20of%20the%20debate%2C%20however%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20defended%20the%20bill%20and%20assured%20everyone%20that%20the%20next%20government%20will%20conduct%20the%20Census%20and%20delimitation%20exercise%20immediately%20after%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20identification%20of%20reserved%20seats%20for%20women%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctransparent%20process%E2%80%9D%20done%20by%20the%20Delimitation%20Commission%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20one%20member%20each%20of%20all%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20Shah%20retorted%20by%20claiming%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20empowerment%20of%20women%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%2C%20not%20a%20political%20weapon%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Cour%20leader%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20too%2C%20in%20his%20inaugural%20speech%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%2C%20had%20said%20that%20he%20had%20been%20chosen%20by%20the%20Almighty%20to%20take%20radical%20steps%20like%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20and%20asserted%20his%20resolve%20to%20strengthen%20women%E2%80%99s%20power.%20Many%20of%20his%20initiatives%20like%20constructing%20toilets%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20or%20even%20the%20Jan%20Dhan%20bank%20accounts%20were%20spun%20by%20the%20BJP%20as%20schemes%20for%20women%2C%20in%20what%20was%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20dedicated%20voting%20constituency%20among%20women.%20In%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20speech%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made%20similar%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20circumstances%2C%20the%20doubts%20raised%20around%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20implementing%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20can%20only%20be%20doused%20by%20the%20BJP.%20That%20a%20greater%20representation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assemblies%20is%20seriously%20%E2%80%9Ca%20matter%20of%20principle%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20PM%20can%20only%20be%20ascertained%20if%20the%20BJP%20takes%20the%20decisive%20step%20to%20field%20women%20candidates%20in%2033%25%20of%20the%20seats%20it%20contests%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20ensuring%20that%2033%25%20of%20its%20candidates%20are%20women%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20not%20only%20assume%20moral%20superiority%20over%20its%20political%20rivals%20but%20also%20send%20out%20an%20unequivocal%20message%20to%20Indian%20women%2C%20who%20could%20be%20in%20a%20state%20of%20confusion%20over%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20regarding%20the%20current%20bill.%20Notwithstanding%20the%20speculations%20over%20the%20bill%E2%80%99s%20implementation%2C%20a%20political%20move%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20nominate%2033%25%20women%20in%20the%20polls%20would%20also%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20natural%20precursor%20to%20what%20the%20bill%20originally%20set%20out%20to%20achieve%2C%20even%20if%20its%20implementation%20is%20delayed%20by%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20led%20by%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20has%20already%20taken%20such%20an%20initiative.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20its%20candidates%20were%20women.%20The%20Odisha%20chief%20minister%20had%20officially%20declared%20that%20the%20radical%20decision%20was%20meant%20to%20show%20his%20resolve%20to%20get%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20passed%20in%20Parliament%2C%20and%20to%20let%20Odisha%20lead%20by%20example%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20reserved%2040%25%20of%20seats%20that%20it%20contested%20for%20women%20candidates%20in%20the%202022%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20elections.%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20state%20unit%E2%80%99s%20president%2C%20showcased%20the%20move%20as%20complementing%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20women-oriented%20election%20campaign%20that%20was%20made%20popular%20by%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ELadki%20hoon%2C%20lad%20sakti%20hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(I%20am%20a%20girl%2C%20and%20I%20can%20fight).%20Some%20other%20Opposition-led%20governments%2C%20including%20Odisha%2C%20have%20also%20passed%20resolutions%20as%20advocacy%20measures%20for%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20too%2C%20has%20a%20stellar%20record%20in%20representing%20women%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20After%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20it%20had%20nearly%2040%25%20women%20MPs.%20In%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20party%20fielded%20women%20candidates%20in%2017%20seats%20of%20the%20total%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20in%20West%20Bengal%20%E2%80%93%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20its%20total%20candidates.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20government%20in%20Kerala%20and%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20government%20in%20Bihar%2C%20apart%20from%20Naveen%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20Odisha%2C%20were%20among%20the%20first%20to%20increase%20the%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20local%20governments%20to%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20only%20a%20poor%20record%20to%20show%20on%20that%20front%2C%20with%20barely%20any%20women%20in%20top%20positions%20of%20the%20governments%20run%20by%20it%20and%20in%20its%20organisational%20set-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20BJP%20walk%20the%20talk%3F%20The%20nation%20seriously%20wants%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695368135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22104636%2FF6kk7dtXkAEhH2a.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fonly-bjp-can-allay-doubts-about-its-commitment-to-womens-reservation-bill%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20parties%20alleged%20that%20the%20bill%20was%20another%20%E2%80%9Celection%C2%A0jumla%E2%80%9D%20ahead%20of%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20five%20states%2C%20and%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20honest%20intention%20to%20implement%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fonly-bjp-can-allay-doubts-about-its-commitment-to-womens-reservation-bill%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Law%20Firm%20Meister%20Seelig%20%26amp%3B%20Fein%20Expands%20to%20West%20Coast%20With%20New%20Los%20Angeles%20Office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695367890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FDuo.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvari