ore%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBishnoi%20was%20the%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cmastermind%E2%80%9D%20behind%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20killing%20last%20year%20and%20is%20currently%20jailed%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20drug%20smuggling%20charges%20that%20are%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fwho-is-lawrence-bishnoi-the-man-behind-the-killing-of-khalistani-terrorist-sukhdool-singh-in-canada%2Farticleshow%2F103832437.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20involved%20in%20gang-related%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%20alongside%20fellow%20gangster%20Goldy%20Brar%20and%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20for%20publicly%20threatening%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20from%20inside%20the%20jail%20during%20a%20news%20interview%20and%20more%20recently%20for%20claiming%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20one%20Sukhdool%20Singh%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20investigating%20officer%20had%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fharyana%2Fmonu-wanted-to-be-part-of-bishnoi-gang-reveal-chats-544737%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Manesar%20made%20several%20calls%2C%20including%20video%2C%20to%20Bishnoi%20between%20August%2028%20and%20September%2010.%20Manesar%20even%20reportedly%20forwarded%20a%20%E2%80%9Cresume%E2%80%9D%20listing%20his%20%E2%80%9Cstature%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cconnections%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20area%2C%20while%20offering%20to%20head%20and%20re-establish%20Bishnoi%E2%80%99s%20network%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBishnoi%20once%20ruled%20the%20extortion%20business%20in%20the%20area%2C%20but%20a%20police%20crackdown%20wiped%20out%20his%20gang.%20Sharing%20a%20common%20interest%20in%20cow%20welfare%2C%20he%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20%E2%80%98gau%20rakshak%E2%80%99%20groups.%20Vigilantes%20like%20Manesar%20caught%20his%20fancy%20after%20the%20Nasir-Junaid%20murder%20case%20and%20Nuh%20clashes.%20He%20wanted%20to%20use%20their%20network%20for%20his%20work.%20From%20group%20chats%2C%20we%20have%20got%20names%20of%20five%20more%20men%20who%20were%20in%20touch%20with%20Bishnoi%2C%20but%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20reveal%20their%20names%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20investigator%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20Tribune%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Manesar%20had%20admitted%20to%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20Bishnoi%2C%20but%20insisted%20that%20it%20was%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98gaushala%E2%80%99%20(cow%20shelter)%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20Hindu%20and%20wanted%20to%20work%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20cows%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20were%20talking.%20The%20conversation%20is%20being%20used%20out%20of%20context%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manesar%20reportedly%20told%20the%20police.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20suspect%20that%20Bishnoi%E2%80%99s%20donations%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98gaushala%E2%80%99%20were%20diverted%20to%20funding%20vigilante%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManesar%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%2C%20Kulbhushan%20Bhardwaj%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20DGP%20said%20Manesar%20was%20not%20a%20murder%20accused%20and%20they%20had%20no%20evidence%20of%20his%20direct%20role%20in%20the%20conspiracy.%20Till%20now%20they%20have%20no%20corroborative%20evidence%20and%20are%20trying%20to%20frame%20him%20for%20links%20with%20gangsters%20whom%20he%20spoke%20to%20just%20for%20welfare%20for%20cows.%20We%20are%20seeking%20legal%20remedies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695367852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22114148%2FUntitled-design-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fpolice-investigation-reveals-links-between-lawrence-bishnoi-and-monu-manesar-other-cow-vigilantes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20information%20reportedly%20came%20to%20light%20after%20the%20police%20arrested%20Man