ion%20request%20first%2C%20before%20seeking%20an%20RCN.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%202016%2C%20a%20PMLA%20court%20had%20allowed%20the%20ED%20to%20begin%20the%20extradition%20process%20against%20Lalit%20Modi.%20All%20extradition%20requests%20are%20routed%20through%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%20But%20as%20per%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1WoqHJS6jdswQ-0aRaAs1MfUGO5DpkTJq%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERTI%20response%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20August%2017%2C%202018%20to%20this%20reporter%2C%20even%20two%20years%20later%2C%20the%20ministry%20had%20not%20received%20a%20formal%20extradition%20request%20from%20any%20law%20enforcement%20agency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EINTERPOL%20also%20noted%20that%20no%20charge%20sheet%20had%20been%20established%20against%20Lalit%20Modi%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INTERPOL%E2%80%99s%20letter%20rejecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20request%20for%20an%20RCN%20against%20Lalit%20Modi%20was%20shared%20by%20him%20on%20Instagram%20in%20March%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBSJdXlcB_Du%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBSJdXlcB_Du%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Lalit%20Modi%20(%40lalitkmodi)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EINTERPOL%20noted%20that%20enquiries%20are%20still%20in%20progress%20concerning%20the%20existence%20of%20direct%20evidence%20to%20factually%20sustain%20the%20allegations%20against%20Lalit%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20a%20Red%20Notice%20is%20not%20to%20obtain%20the%20transfer%20of%20a%20person%20in%20order%20to%20assist%20in%20an%20investigation%20or%20give%20evidence%20in%20proceedings.%20Its%20purpose%20rather%20is%20to%20facilitate%20the%20seeking%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20extradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBSJdXlcB_Du%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecopy%20of%20the%20order%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20shared%20by%20Lalit%20Modi%20on%20social%20media%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChennai%20Police%E2%80%99s%20FIR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Chennai%20Police%20investigation%20also%20appears%20to%20have%20made%20zero%20progress%2C%20even%20after%20seven%20years.%20Since%20the%20investigation%20had%20seemingly%20not%20taken%20off%2C%20a%20formal%20charge%20sheet%20against%20Modi%20was%20not%20filed%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20ED%20to%20prove%20charges%20of%20money%20laundering%2C%20the%20law%20requires%20the%20original%20offence%2C%20called%20predicate%20offence%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%20the%20FIR%20filed%20before%20the%20Chennai%20Police%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20firmly%20established.%20This%20is%20because%20if%20a%20person%20who%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20committed%20criminal%20activity%20by%20way%20of%20an%20FIR%20is%20found%20innocent%2C%20any%20benefit%20he%20derives%20as%20a%20result%20of%20such%20innocent%20activity%20cannot%20be%20termed%20laundering%20of%20tainted%20money%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20a%20money%20laundering%20charge%20cannot%2C%20naturally%2C%20survive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Chennai%20Police%20FIR%20is%20the%20only%20predicate%20offence%20against%20Lalit%20Modi%2C%20it%20was%20crucial%20that%20the%20police%20conclude%20their%20investigation%20and%20file%20charge%20sheets%2C%20thus%20creating%20sufficient%20%E2%80%9Cjudicial%20data%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20charge%20sheet%20in%20the%20predicate%20offence%20is%20also%20mandatory%20for%20all%20extradition%20requests%20made%20to%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20March%202017%2C%20a%20day%20after%20INTERPOL%20conveyed%20its%20rejection%2C%20the%20then%20ED%20director%20Karnal%20Singh%2C%20visibly%20frustrated%2C%20sent%20a%20strongly-worded%20letter%20to%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20noted%20that%20the%20Chennai%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Crime%20Branch%20had%20not%20shared%20any%20progress%20on%20the%20Lalit%20Modi%20case%20despite%20repeated%20requests.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20inability%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20in%20logically%20concluding%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20case%20is%20causing%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20Law%20Enforcement%20Agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20further%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThings%20moved%20after%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20was%20quickly%20transferred%20to%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20(CB%20CID)%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police.%20In%20July%202017%2C%20on%20the%20state%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20advice%2C%20the%20police%20declared%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20territorial%20jurisdiction%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20case%20and%20recommended%20its%20transfer%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20or%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20however%2C%20declined%20to%20take%20over%2C%20citing%20the%20FIR%E2%80%99s%20origin%20in%20Chennai%2C%20and%20returned%20the%20case%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20again%20seeking%20the%20state%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20opinion%2C%20on%20October%2031%2C%202017%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20recommended%20a%20CBI%20probe%20and%20requested%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20allow%20the%20takeover.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14132633%2FScreenshot-2023-09-13-at-15.34.13.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14132633%2FScreenshot-2023-09-13-at-15.34.13.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14132633%2FScreenshot-2023-09-13-at-15.34.13-300x226.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14132633%2FScreenshot-2023-09-13-at-15.34.13-1024x771.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22903%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%E2%80%99s%20proforma%20submitted%20to%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20seeking%20CBI%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20the%20Union%20government%20did%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%2