eriorating%E2%80%9D%20rights%20situation%20in%20India%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FFernand%2520de%2520Varennes%2520Testimony.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cmassive%2C%20systematic%20and%20dangerous%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opening%20remarks%20at%20a%20hearing%20on%20policy%20options%20for%20advancing%20religious%20freedom%20in%20India%2C%20organised%20by%20the%20US%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20(USCIRF)%20in%20Washington%20DC%20on%20September%2020%2C%202023%2C%20De%20Varennes%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20risks%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20main%20generators%20of%20instability%2C%20atrocities%20and%20violence%2C%20because%20of%20the%20massive%20scale%20and%20gravity%20of%20the%20violations%20and%20abuses%20targeting%20mainly%20religious%20and%20other%20minorities%20such%20as%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%2C%20Sikhs%20and%20others.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20individual%20or%20local%2C%20it%20is%20systematic%20and%20a%20reflection%20of%20religious%20nationalism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-qIJ-pew2ZI%3Fsi%3DMlIkkDxflSEa7UIr%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20of%20how%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20issued%20numerous%20communications%20and%20press%20releases%2C%20communications%20being%20way%20allegations%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20raised%20though%20diplomatic%20channels%20to%20the%20concerned%20governments.%20They%20show%20a%20steady%20and%20alarming%20erosion%20of%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20particularly%20for%20religious%20and%20other%20minorities%20from%20the%20review%20of%20communications%20from%202011%20to%20now%3A%20By%202022%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20involve%20grave%20allegations%20of%20denial%20of%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20particularly%20targeting%20religious%20minorities.%20From%2012%20May%202020%20to%2023%20May%202023%2C%20around%2046%20communications%20and%20an%20estimated%2020%20press%20releases.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Special%20Rapporteur%20invoked%20Manipur%20several%20times%2C%20and%20the%20viral%20video%20of%20an%20incident%20on%20May%204%2C%20which%20shows%20a%20mob%20and%20two%20women%20disrobed%20and%20made%20to%20march%20on%20the%20road.%20Varennes%20said%20that%20two%20women%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20the%20Christian%20Kuki%20community%20%5Bwere%5D%20being%20paraded%20naked%2C%20beaten%20and%20gang%20raped%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20was%20inaction%20from%20authorities%20until%20this%20video%20caught%20the%20international%20attention%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20Manipur%20as%20being%20%E2%80%9Csymptomatic%20of%20large-scale%20scapegoating%20and%20dehumanising%20of%20Muslims%20and%20religious%20%E2%80%98others%E2%80%99%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20slide%20towards%20horrific%20atrocities%E2%80%9D.%20He%20cited%20a%20study%20which%20%E2%80%9Cnoted%20a%20786%25%20increase%20in%20hate%20crimes%20against%20minorities%20between%202014%20and%202018%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cdiscriminatory%20citizenship%20determination%20process%20in%20Assam%2C%20and%20potentially%20other%20regions%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20millions%20denied%20citizenship%2C%E2%80%9D%20especially%20Muslims%20came%20up.%20As%20did%20the%20revocation%20in%202019%20%E2%80%9Cof%20the%20special%20status%20or%20autonomy%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDe%20Varennes%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20national%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20early%202024%2C%20there%20are%20concerns%20that%20the%20targeting%20of%20minorities%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%20will%20worsen.%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20not%20taken%20any%20tangible%20steps%20to%20hold%20perpetrators%20of%20abuses%20against%20minorities%20to%20account.%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20not%20engaged%20constructively%20with%20criticism%2C%20boasting%20instead%20of%20democratic%20values%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20Some%20senior%20leaders%20have%20either%20remained%20silent%2C%20or%20have%20indeed%20contributed%2C%20through%20their%20own%20rhetoric%2C%20to%20the%20hostile%20environment%20against%20religious%20minorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20actions%20of%20Canada%20in%20response%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20came%20up%20at%20the%20hearing.%20The%20UN%20Special%20Rapporteur%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20slain%20man%20was%20a%20Sikh%20and%20a%20member%20of%20a%20religious%20minority%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20going%20into%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20charges%E2%80%9D%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Can%20important%20message%20to%20India%20that%20certain%20type%20of%20conduct%20is%20not%20acceptable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20pressure%E2%80%9D%20especially%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment%20to%20government%E2%80%9D%20pressure%20and%20from%20the%20US%20and%20allies%20to%20force%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cchange%20certain%20policies%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cto%20change%20direction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20parallel%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20status%20of%20religious%20freedoms%20in%20Tajikistan%2C%20a%20country%20recognised%20as%20being%20one%20of%20special%20concern%2C%20by%20the%20UN%20Special%20Rapporteur%20who%20said%20Tajikistan%20%E2%80%9Cpales%20when%20we%20look%20at%20massive%20atrocities%20in%20India%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20denial%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20US%20in%20June%20and%20was%20asked%20in%20his%20first%20press%20conference%20as%20prime%20minister%20where%20he%20took%20one%20question%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20about%20religious%20freedoms%2C%20status%20of%20minorities%20and%20free%20speech%20in%20India%2C%20he%20said%20democracy%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20in%20the%20DNA%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20US%20and%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2023%2F06%2F22%2Fremarks-by-president-biden-and-prime-minister-modi-of-the-republic-of-india-in-joint-press-conference%2F%5C%22%3EHe%20further%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20always%20proved%20that%20democracy%20can%20deliver.%20And%20when%20I%20say%20deliver%2C%20this%20is%20regardless%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%2C%20religion%2C%20gender.%C2%A0%20There%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20no%20space%20for%20discrimination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202022%20Annual%20Report%2C%20USCIRF%20recommended%20that%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20designate%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccountry%20of%20particular%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20for%20engaging%20in%20or%20tolerating%20systematic%2C%20ongoing%2C%20and%20egregious%20religious%20freedom%20violations%2C%20as%20set%20forth%20by%20the%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695353783000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F16150815%2FFernand-de-Varennes.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fun-expert-says-india-risks-becoming-one-of-the-main-generators-of-instability-atrocities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20USCIRF%20Hearing%20on%20Religious%20Freedom%20in%20India%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20there%20was%20talk%20of%20Manipur%2C%20Assam%20and%20discriminatory%20laws%20and%20processes%20for%20religious%20and%20other%20minorities%20and%20%E2%80%9Ca%20steady%20and%20alarming%20erosion%20of%20fundamental%20rights%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fun-expert-says-india-risks-becoming-one-of-the-main-generators-of-instability-atrocities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Date%20Set%20for%20Implementation%20as%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20Is%20Passed%20Unanimously%20by%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22085539%2FF6kk7dvXIAAUkKk.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Two%20days%20after%20it%20was%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhistoric-day-says-pm-modi-as-he-announces-womens-reservation-bill-in-new-parliament%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20that%20seeks%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20unanimously%20on%20Thursday%20(September%2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Bill%20is%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%2C%20it%20will%20need%20to%20be%20ratified%20by%20half%20of%20the%20state%20legislatures%20before%20it%20can%20be%20sent%20for%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20assent%20to%20become%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20was%20passed%20with%20215%20members%20voting%20in%20favour%20and%20none%20opposing%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20debate%20that%20lasted%20over%20ten%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20with%20speeches%20from%2072%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20legislation%20was%20passed%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20specific%20timeline%20of%20when%20the%20law%20would%20be%20implemented%2C%20even%20as%20opposition%20members%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20delimitation%20and%20census%20clause%20tied%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-womens-reservation-bill-amit-shah-implementation-2029%5C%22%3Epassed%20the%20legislation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20works%20for%2027%20years%2C%20with%20a%20two-thirds%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Bill%20was%20put%20to%20vote%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20to%20thank%20all%20members%20for%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlmost%20132%20speakers%20have%20spoken%20in%20both%20houses.%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20all%20members%20for%20supporting%20the%20Bill.%20This%20spirit%20that%20has%20been%20born%2C%20will%20create%20a%20new%20spirit%20of%20self%20confidence%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20consciousness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20MPs%2C%20and%20political%20parties%20have%20played%20an%20important%20role%E2%80%A6and%20this%20itself%20will%20be%20a%20guarantee%20of%20our%20bright%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20states%20that%20one-third%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20by%20amending%20Article%20239AA%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20amending%20Article%20330%2C%20and%20in%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20by%20amending%20Article%20332.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20480px)%2085vw%2C%20480px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22103038%2Fimage-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22103038%2Fimage-1.png%20480w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22103038%2Fimage-1-120x300.png%20120w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22103038%2Fimage-1-410x1024.png%20410w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674223%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBill%20passed%2C%20no%20specific%20timeline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20unanimous%20support%20given%20to%20the%20legislation%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20failed%20to%20provide%20a%20specific%20timeline%20for%20its%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20states%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprovisions%20relating%20to%20the%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20women%E2%80%A6shall%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20an%20exercise%20of%20delimitation%20is%20undertaken%20for%20this%20purpose%20after%20the%20relevant%20figures%20for%20the%20first%20census%20taken%20after%20%5Bthe%20Bill%20is%20passed%5D%20have%20been%20published.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20her%20reply%20to%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20opposition%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20is%20not%20an%20%E2%80%9Celection%20%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20bill%20is%20not%20a%20%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Delimitation%20is%20not%20an%20exercise%20to%20push%20this%20exercise%20further.%20Once%20we%20pass%20this%20(Bill)%2C%20and%20the%20census%20takes%20place%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20set%20rolling%20for%20a%20delimitation%20commission%20to%20come%20into%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-delimitation-prudent-pragmatic-approach%5C%22%3Efreeze%20on%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20till%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccarrying%20a%20legacy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%202026%20stand%20out%20for%20us%3F%20We%20are%20carrying%20a%20legacy%20where%20delimitation%20dates%20have%20been%20frozen%20not%20once%20but%20twice%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time.%20With%20these%20realities%20it%20will%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20implement%20it%20now.%20Once%20the%20census%20is%20over%2C%20and%20the%20delimitation%20is%20done%2C%20we%20will%20implement%20this%20(Bill)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20in%20his%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20stated%20that%20the%20legislation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-womens-reservation-bill-amit-shah-implementation-2029%5C%22%3Ewill%20not%20come%20into%20force%20till%202029.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20position%20in%20his%20reply%20while%20putting%20the%20bill%20to%20vote%2C%20union%20minister%20for%20law%20and%20justice%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C..Do%20not%20worry%20(about%20implementation)%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3EModi%20hai%20toh%20mumkin%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(With%20Modi%2C%20it%20is%20all%20possible).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20raised%20by%20the%20opposition%20about%20the%20delay%20in%20bringing%20in%20the%20legislation%20in%20the%209.5%20years%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20in%20power%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbuild%20consensus%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20that%20we%20build%20consensus%20and%20also%20show%20that%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20the%20economic%20and%20social%20empowerment%20of%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20also%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20government%20was%20working%20to%20uplift%20women%20socially%20and%20economically%20and%20referred%20to%20government%20schemes%20like%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%2C%20Mudra%20loan%20scheme%2C%20and%20incorporating%20women%20into%20combat%20roles%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestions%20over%20delay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%2C%20however%2C%20questioned%20the%20delimitation%20and%20census%20clause%20and%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20delaying%20the%20legislation%E2%80%99s%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20and%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20demanded%20a%20specific%20date%20for%20the%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20the%20commitment%20then%20give%20us%20the%20month%2C%20give%20us%20the%20year%20(when%20it%20will%20be%20implemented.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20it%20will%20be%20a%20jumla%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20BJP%20MP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20that%20the%20legislation%20was%20not%20passed%20by%20the%20UPA%20government%20despite%20it%20being%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20should%20rectify%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFine%E2%80%A6if%20we%20did%20not%20do%20it%E2%80%A6okay%20it%20was%20our%20mistake%20but%20you%20can%20rectify%20it.%20Only%20giving%20%3Cem%3Ebhashan%20(%3C%2Fem%3Esermons)%20is%20not%20enough.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20MP%20and%20now%20independent%20Kapil%20Sibal%20demanded%20resignations%20from%20the%20home%20minister%20and%20prime%20minister%20if%20the%20implementation%20date%20is%20not%20seen%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%20(on%20the%20date)%20and%20if%20it%20is%20not%20done%20they%20will%20resign.%20At%20least%20they%20should%20give%20an%20assurance%20at%20least%20that%20it%20will%20be%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20questioned%20the%20government%20for%20staying%20away%20from%20immediate%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBring%20the%202010%20Bill%20which%20gave%20immediate%20representation.%20There%20is%20no%20law%20in%20the%20world%20that%20comes%20into%20effect%20seven%20years%20later.%20With%20this%20Bill%20we%20are%20opening%20the%20door%20but%20(telling%20women)%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20give%20entry%20for%20the%20next%207.5%20years.%20What%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20immediate%20implementation%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20question%20and%20the%20exclusion%20of%20OBC%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20the%20previous%20day%2C%20opposition%20members%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20also%20reiterated%20the%20demand%20for%20sub-quotas%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20along%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20OBC%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERJD%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20made%20a%20strong%20pitch%20for%20sub-quotas%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20surname%20gives%20us%20our%20privilege%E2%80%A6In%20this%20country%2C%20perhaps%20there%20is%20nothing%20in%20a%20name%20but%20everything%20is%20there%20in%20a%20surname%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%202008%20delimitation%20commission%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20412%20general%20seats%2C%2084%20SC%20seats%20and%2047%20ST%20seats%2C%20Through%20this%20bill%20we%20will%20make%20this%201%2F3%20of%2084%20and%2047.%20Is%20this%20not%20injustice%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20not%20giving%2033%25%20across%20the%20board%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20not%20giving%20to%20SC-ST%20and%20OBC%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJha%20said%20that%20the%20bill%20could%20still%20include%20OBC%20women%20by%20sending%20it%20to%20a%20select%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20members%20of%20the%20AIMIM%20on%20Wednesday%20were%20the%20only%20two%20MPs%20who%20had%20voted%20against%20the%20Bill%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Canti-Muslim%E2%80%9D%20and%20anti-OBC%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20need%20for%20including%20reservation%20for%20OBC%20was%20also%20demanded%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20JMM%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20BSP%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYSRCP%20MP%20Ryaga%20Krishnaiah%20said%20without%20sub-quotas%2C%20the%20Bill%20will%20not%20be%20meaningful.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGeneral%20discrimination%20will%20come%20down%20with%20this%20bill%20but%20to%20reduce%20caste%20discrimination%20I%20want%20to%20suggest%2C%20provide%20a%20sub%20quota%20to%20OBC%20women.%20Without%20it%20this%20bill%20will%20not%20be%20meaningful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdityanath%2C%20Manipur%20and%20price%20rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20two%20opposition%20members%20cited%20quotes%20by%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20to%20target%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETMC%20MP%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20said%20that%20the%20question%20is%20if%20the%20BJP%20is%20serious%20about%20empowerment%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20struggles%20of%20women%20are%20not%20because%20of%20women%20but%20because%20of%20men%20and%20their%20outlook%20of%20women.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20waste%20my%20time%20on%20a%20former%20wrestling%20chief%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20alluding%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20harassment%20by%20seven%20female%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20read%20out%20an%20alleged%20quote%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20from%20a%20media%20report%20that%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20air-conditioned%20rooms%20in%20Delhi%20cannot%20decide%20public%20policy.%20This%20Bill%20will%20drown%20the%20Indian%20political%20system%20if%20it%20goes%20through.%20If%20men%20develop%20feminine%20traits%2C%20they%20become%20Gods.%20If%20women%20develop%20feminine%20traits%2C%20they%20become%20%3Cem%3Erakshasas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Western%20ideas%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20liberation%20should%20be%20properly%20analysed%20in%20Indian%20context.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%20then%20asked%20him%20to%20provide%20documents%20to%20prove%20his%20claims%20by%20the%20course%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20KC%20Venugopal%20also%20referred%20to%20Adityanath%20in%20his%20speech%20and%20cited%20a%20quote%20from%20when%20he%20was%20Gorakhpur%20MP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20reservation%20for%20women%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20How%20does%20it%20impact%20the%20other%20responsibilities%20of%20women%20such%20as%20childcare.%20It%20should%20be%20assessed%20whether%20women%E2%80%99s%20quota%20affects%20these%20roles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20quoted%20Adityanath%20as%20saying%20from%20a%20news%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20means%20your%20attitude%20is%20that%20women%20are%20meant%20for%20childcare%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20two%20Kuki%20women%20who%20were%20paraded%20naked%20in%20Manipur%20in%20May%20during%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20pained%20to%20see%20the%20women%20paraded%20naked%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20women%20cried%20in%20front%20of%20us..in%20100%20days%20PM%20had%20not%20spoken.%20You%20are%20talking%20about%20women%20empowerment..What%20women%20empowerment%3F%20Why%20is%20Nirbhaya%20fund%20unutilised%3F%20Give%20us%20the%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20in%20a%20very%20difficult%20situation%20in%20this%20country%20due%20to%20price%20rise%E2%80%A6LPG%20gas%20is%20Rs%201000%20a%20cylinder%2C%20petrol%2C%20tomato%E2%80%A6price%20rise%20everywhere%E2%80%A6their%20security%20is%20totally%20compromised%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETempers%20also%20flared%20in%20the%20house%20when%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20referred%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20ahead%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20elections%20where%20he%20called%20out%20to%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20as%20%E2%80%9CDidi%20O%20Didi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20Modi%2C%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20men%20came%20with%20money%2C%20the%20media%2C%20with%20muscle%20power%2C%20with%20misogyny%20and%20mocked%20her%2C%20Didi%2C%20O%20Didi.%20You%20even%20tried%20to%20smash%20and%20you%20broke%20her%20foot%E2%80%A6to%20injure%20her.%20She%20gave%20you%20the%20answer%20truly%20like%20a%20woman%2C%20softly.%20The%20people%20of%20Bengal%20in%20India%20provided%20the%20answer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDhankar%20took%20objection%20to%20O%E2%80%99Brien%E2%80%99s%20comments%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20place%20documents%20in%20the%20house%20on%20who%20he%20meant%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20men%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695353188000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22085539%2FF6kk7dvXIAAUkKk.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-date-set-for-implementation-as-womens-reservation-bill-is-passed-unanimously-by-rajya-sabha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bill%20was%20passed%20with%20215%20members%20voting%20in%20favour%20and%20none%20opposing%2C%20as%20opposition%20members%20questioned%20the%20delimitation%20and%20census%20clause%20tied%20to%20it%20and%20demanded%20a%20date%20for%20implementation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-date-set-for-implementation-as-womens-reservation-bill-is-passed-unanimously-by-rajya-sabha%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20reserves%20third%20of%20Parliament%20seats%20for%20women%20-%20but%20nothing%20will%20change%20soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695352491000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F12ECB%2Fproduction%2F_131151577_gettyimages-1245406307-594x594.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66878565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decades-old%20bill%20guarantees%20a%