0use%20the%20application%20to%20navigate%20to%20a%20CNG%2Fpetrol%2Fdiesel%20station%20on%20your%20route%2C%20or%20find%20one%20closest%20to%20you.%20We%20have%20more%20than%20a%20million%20downloads%20on%20the%20app%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav%2C%20co-founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20Nawgati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%204-year-old%20app%20is%20currently%20free%2C%20but%20the%20founders%20have%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20freemium%20model%20soon%2C%20where%20they%20would%20offer%20basic%20features%20for%20free%2C%20but%20charge%20for%20the%20premium%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20had%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%202%20and%20signed%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2067%20lakhs%20for%203%20percent%20equity.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20Nawgati%20and%20led%20to%20more%20dealers%20reaching%20out%20to%20them.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20backed%20by%20the%20department%20of%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20revolutionising%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%2C%20benefiting%20both%20fuel%20providers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%20Any%20new%20CNG%20station%20is%20now%20listed%20on%20our%20app%20too.%20This%20helps%20fuel%20stations%20get%20more%20sales.%20We%20have%2075000%20fuel%20stations%20listed%20on%20the%20app%20today.%20We%20are%20fuel%20agnostic%2C%20and%20also%20list%20EV%20charging%20stations%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERun%20by%20two%2025-year-olds%20and%20one%2024-year-old%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20become%20synonymous%20with%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20Nawgati%20to%20be%20the%20doctor%20for%20any%20fuel%20related%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vaibhav.%20Now%2C%20when%20Vaibav%20hops%20onto%20a%20cab%2C%20he%20leads%20the%20driver%20to%20the%20nearest%20fuel%20station%20with%20the%20least%20waiting%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218288000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nawgati%2C%20founded%20by%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%2C%20Aryan%20Sisodia%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%2C%20wants%20to%20change%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%20in%20India.%20Its%20B2B%20platform%20'Aaveg'%20offers%20congestion%20monitoring%20through%20technology%20for%20fuel%20stations%20while%20the%20app%20offers%20easy%20navigation%20for%20customers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330313%2Fnawgati-fuelling-management-app-innovative-startup-shark-tank-india-bits-pilani%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Royal%20Physician%20and%20Freedom%20Fighter%20%26amp%3B%20The%20Story%20Behind%20India%E2%80%99s%20Oldest%20Ganeshotsav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20that%20time%20of%20the%20year%20when%20houses%20across%20the%20country%20are%20adorned%20with%20flowers%20and%20festive%20lights%20to%20welcome%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295735%2Feasy-eco-friendly-home-decor-ideas-for-ganesh-chaturthi-on-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ganapati%20%3Cem%3EBappa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20do%20you%20know%20the%20origin%20story%20of%20how%20this%20iconic%20festival%20came%20into%20existence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20go%20back%20about%20131%20years.%20During%20a%20time%20when%20India%20was%20actively%20resisting%20British%20colonial%20rule%20and%20striving%20for%20independence%2C%20Krishnajipant%20Khasgiwale%20used%20the%20festival%20to%20demonstrate%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201892%2C%20Pune%20resident%20Krishnajipant%20visited%20the%20Maratha-ruled%20Gwalior.%20There%2C%20he%20witnessed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261898%2Findias-oldest-ganeshotsav-was-set-up-by-a-freedom-fighter-in-1892%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20public%20celebration%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20his%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Shrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%20and%20Balasaheb%20Natu%20%E2%80%94%20back%20home%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%2C%20also%20a%20famous%20royal%20physician%20and%20a%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20saw%20potential%20in%20this%20festival%20to%20unite%20countrymen.%20So%20he%20installed%20the%20first%20%3Cem%3Esaarvajanik%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20public%20Ganesha%20idol%20in%20his%20home%20or%20%3Cem%3Ewada%3C%2Fem%3E%20located%20in%20an%20area%20called%20Shalukar%20Bol.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20was%20unique%20as%20it%20depicted%20the%20deity%20killing%20a%20demon.%20Made%20of%20wood%20and%20bran%2C%20the%20imagery%20was%20far%20from%20the%20usual%20calm%20and%20composed%20demeanour%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261867%2Fhow-to-carve-clay-ganesh-idol-chathurthi-sustainable-hack-eco-friendly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20Lord%20Ganesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20this%20was%20symbolic%20of%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20fighting%20for%20its%20freedom%20against%20the%20colonialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20gained%20more%20attention%20when%20freedom%20fighter%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20praised%20his%20efforts%20in%20an%20article%20in%20the%20iconic%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EKesari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Over%20a%20century%20later%2C%20the%20original%20idol%20made%20of%20paper%20pulp%20is%20still%20worshipped%20at%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%E2%80%99s%20wada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDid%20you%20find%20the%20story%20interesting%3F%20Watch%20this%20short%20video%20to%20find%20out%20more%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAu35GJHjHWE%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218070000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fimg.youtube.com%2Fvi%2FAu35GJHjHWE%2F0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20royal%20physician%20and%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20Shrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%20installed%20a%20unique%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ganesha%20in%20India's%20first%20public%20%E2%80%98Ganeshotsav%E2%80%99%20to%20send%20the%20British%20a%20strong%20message%20of%20India's%20unity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330388%2Forigin-story-oldest-public-ganeshotsav-freedom-fighter-pune-ganesha-chaturthi-video%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20India%20Can%20Learn%20From%20TN%20%26amp%3B%20MP%E2%80%99s%20Policies%20to%20Build%20Inclusive%20Schools%20Across%20the%20Country%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20published%20in%20collaboration%20with%20EkStep%20Foundation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%2025%20years%20of%20working%20in%20the%20field%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325086%2Fhow-does-inclusive-education-in-early-childhood-development-help-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einclusive%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20Sonali%20Saini%20privy%20to%20a%20glaring%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20India%20lacks%20inclusive%20policies%20and%20frameworks.%20The%20issue%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20massive%20struggle%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20on%20inclusion%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3Ehow%20do%20we%20make%20inclusive%20schools%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20inclusivity%20and%20subsequently%20good%20learning%20opportunities%2C%20India%20faces%20a%20grave%20problem%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20early%20childhood%20care%20and%20development.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%20highlights%20that%20over%20five%20crore%20children%20currently%20in%20elementary%20school%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309309%2Fcentral-square-foundation-teachers-guide-improves-learning-outcomes-nipun-bharat-mission%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20attained%20foundational%20literacy%20and%20numeracy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20current%20educational%20system%20is%20such%2C%20it%20adds%2C%20that%20once%20a%20student%20falls%20behind%20on%20this%20foundational%20learning%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20maintain%20a%20flat%20learning%20curve%20for%20years%2C%20perpetually%20unable%20to%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20Sonali%20and%20her%20organisation%20Sol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%20have%20worked%20to%20understand%20this%20problem%20in%20depth.%20In%202003%2C%20she%20founded%20the%20non-profit%20to%20build%20inclusive%20education%20and%20livelihood%20solutions%20that%20use%20innovative%20tools%20to%20encourage%20better%20learning%20and%20life%20outcomes.%20They%20aim%20to%20make%20these%20solutions%20scalable%2C%20so%20they%20may%20be%20deployed%20through%20partnerships%20with%20stakeholders%20like%20other%20NGOs%2C%20the%20government%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20has%20been%20about%20%5Bfiguring%20out%5D%20what%20an%20inclusive%20school%20looks%20like%20in%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20very%20high%20resources%2C%20where%20even%20%5Bprocuring%5D%20crayons%2C%20chairs%2C%20tables%20is%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sonali%20explains%20in%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20impacted%20four%20million%20children%20and%20young%20adults%20with%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sonali%20founded%20the%20non-profit%20SOL's%20Arc%20to%20build%20inclusive%20education%20and%20livelihood%20solutions.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484.jpg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330351%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESonali%20founded%20the%20non-profit%20Sol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%20to%20build%20inclusive%20education%20and%20livelihood%20solutions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20%E2%80%98lifespan%20approach%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20been%20notable%20about%20Sol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20its%20collaboration%20with%20state%20governments%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20improve%20foundational%20literacy%20and%20inclusive%20education.%20These%20interventions%20serve%20as%20examples%20of%20how%20the%20reach%20and%20implementation%20of%20existing%20policies%20can%20be%20widened%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311679%2Fthings-to-know-jaadui-pitara-play-based-learning-children-national-curriculum-framework%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpact%20lakhs%20of%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20there%20is%20Project%20Ankur%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20building%20Foundational%20Literacy%20(English)%C2%A0%20and%20Numeracy%20(Math)%20through%20an%20inclusive%20curriculum%20for%20teachers%20and%20students%20from%20Class%201%20to%20Class%203.%20This%20has%20been%20done%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Rajya%20Shiksha%20Kendra%2C%20the%20key%20department%20working%20towards%20the%20state%20FLN%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%20analyses%20that%20non-inclusive%20pedagogy%2C%20non-conceptual%20FLN%20frameworks%2C%20and%20low%20teacher%20capacities%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20why%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20vulnerable%20children%20are%20not%20learning%20as%20they%20should.%20Sonali%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20look%20at%20%5Bhigh-income%5D%20countries%2C%20their%20solutions%20were%20very%20high%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20assistive%20technology%2C%20accessible%20content%E2%80%A6that%20may%20not%20be%20possible%20in%20a%20country%20like%20ours%2C%20which%20has%20low%20digital%20penetration.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20teacher%20ratio%20and%20the%20special%20educator%20ratios%20are%20abysmal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20Government%20data%20suggests%20that%20the%20teacher%20ratio%20has%20fallen%20from%2043%20in%202010-11%20to%2026.3%20in%202020-%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%2C%20she%20says%2C%20focuses%20more%20on%20education%20outcomes%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20subsequently%20increase%20livelihood%20opportunities.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20on%20a%20lifespan%20approach%20because%20only%20working%20on%20education%20may%20not%20be%20sufficient.%20Even%20when%20we%20complete%20education%2C%20if%20the%20children%20are%20still%20sitting%20at%20home%2C%20then%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20point.%20So%20to%20improve%20life%20outcomes%2C%20we%20include%20that%20under%20our%20focus%20for%20age%20groups%20from%205-39.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation's%20UDL%20approach%20emphasises%20flexible%20learning%20environments%20that%20accommodate%20individual%20learning%20differences.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330354%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20UDL%20approach%20emphasises%20flexible%20learning%20environments%20that%20accommodate%20individual%20learning%20differences.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMultiple%20children%2C%20multiple%20ways%20to%20learn%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Project%20Ankur%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20taken%20on%20a%20Universal%20Design%20for%20Learning%20(UDL)%20approach%20to%20teaching%20and%20learning%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cgives%20all%20students%20equal%20opportunities%20to%20succeed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUDL%20is%20a%20framework%20that%20emphasises%20flexible%20learning%20environments%20that%20accommodate%20individual%20learning%20differences.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20basically%20says%20%E2%80%98Teach%20in%20multiple%20ways%2C%20allow%20the%20child%20to%20respond%20in%20multiple%20ways%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6the%20teaching-learning%20material%20should%20have%20multiple%20modalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonali.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20aims%20to%20bring%20flexibility%20in%20these%20arenas%20so%20they%20can%20be%20adjusted%20as%20per%20an%20individual%20learner%E2%80%99s%20strengths%20and%20needs.%20They%20say%20this%20is%20a%20low-tech%2C%20low-cost%20approach%20that%20is%20suitable%20for%20low-resource%20classrooms%20in%20India.%20The%20resources%20to%20teach%20include%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20adaptable%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20to%20teach%20subtraction%2C%20a%20teacher%20may%20use%20blocks%2C%20number%20lines%2C%20adapted%20worksheets%2C%20and%20flash%20cards.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20you%E2%80%99ve%20exposed%20the%20child%20to%20all%20learning%20methods%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20the%20child%20which%20way%20they%20want%20to%20carry%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sonali%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20also%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F234203%2Fnew-national-education-policy-2020-pdf-report-cards-marks-grades-score-cce-continuous-evaluation-descriptive-indicators-sai87%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20ways%20of%20assessment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20way%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20allowing%20different%20children%20with%20different%20abilities%20to%20answer%20the%20same%20question%20in%20their%20own%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20a%20child%20is%20non-verbal%2C%20the%20schools%20are%20not%20relying%20on%20oral%20examinations%20alone.%20Instead%2C%20the%20child%20can%20respond%20by%20pointing%20at%20the%20right%20answer%20or%20writing%20it%20down.%20If%20the%20child%20has%20challenges%20in%20reading%2C%20then%20the%20child%20may%20receive%20assistance%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20reader.%20%E2%80%9CInstructions%20are%20broken%20down%2C%20turned%20into%20visuals%E2%80%A6then%20all%20children%20benefit%20with%20these%20interventions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20also%20addressed%20the%20challenge%20of%20multi-grade%20classrooms%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304738%2Fnational-curriculum-framework-for-foundational-stage-education-children-india-ekstep%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreaking%20the%20curriculum%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20types%20of%20learning%20environments%20can%20be%20challenging%20owing%20to%20monograde%20teaching%20material%2C%20low%20availability%20of%20teachers%2C%20rigid%20timetables%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20estimates%20that%20approximately%2078%25%20of%20primary%20schools%20in%20India%20have%20three%20or%20fewer%20teachers%20for%20all%20grade%20levels.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20made%20multi-grade%20plans%2C%20wherein%20we%20say%20here%20are%20your%20common%20activities%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20you%20will%20do%20separately%2C%20and%20that%20way%20we%20address%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20teachers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20EkStep%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695190027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330342%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sonali%20Saini%20and%20her%20organisation%20Sol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%20have%20worked%20with%20the%20governments%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20implement%20several%20scalable%2C%20low-cost%2C%20and%20replicable%20policies%20for%20inclusive%20education.%20She%20explains%20why%20these%20could%20be%20key%20in%20transforming%20the%20early%20childhood%20care%20ecosystem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Divya%20Sethu%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330342%2Ftamil-nadu-madhya-pradesh-policies-for-inclusive-education-improve-early-childhood-care-sonali-saini-sols-arc%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%E2%80%99s%20Unique%20Tech%20Can%20Turn%2010%20Tonnes%20of%20Wet%20Waste%20Into%20Compost%20In%20Just%208%20Hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffactly.in%2Freview-municipal-solid-waste-generated-in-india-set-to-increase-7-times-in-the-next-30-years%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCurrently%252C%2520as%2520per%2520government%2520estimates%2C%252C%2520wood%252C%2520glass%252C%2520etc.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20estimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20dating%20back%20to%202021%2C%20India%20generates%20more%20than%2062%20million%20tonnes%20of%20Municipal%20Solid%20Waste%20(MSW)%2C%20of%20which%20approximately%2075-80%25%20gets%20collected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20amount%20of%20MSW%20collected%2C%20only%20about%2022-28%25%20is%20processed%20and%20treated.%20The%20rest%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills.%20Going%20further%2C%20up%20to%20half%20the%20MSW%20collected%20in%20India%20consists%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbiodegradable%20(organic)%20matter%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmohua.gov.in%2Fupload%2Fuploadfiles%2Ffiles%2F93.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMinistry%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20scale%20of%20this%20problem%2C%20there%20are%20multiple%20ventures%20across%20different%20Indian%20cities%20arriving%20at%20different%20scalable%20solutions%20to%20treat%20organic%20MSW.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%E2%80%98Waste%20Is%20Gold%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20waste%20management%20company%2C%20is%20one%20such%20venture%20which%20has%20arrived%20at%20a%20unique%20technological%20solution%20to%20address%20this%20pressing%20waste%20management%20concern.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalled%20the%20%E2%80%98Gold%20Composter%E2%80%99%2C%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301152%2Fbengaluru-designer-builds-home-composter-mess-free-odourless-daily-dump-waste-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20waste%20composter%3C%2Fa%3E%20possesses%20an%20impressive%20capability%20of%20%E2%80%9Cseamlessly%20converting%E2%80%9D%20waste%20amounting%20to%20anywhere%20between%2020%20kg%20to%2010%20tonnes%20into%20%E2%80%98nutrient-rich%20compost%E2%80%99%20in%20just%20eight%20hours%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20emitting%20harmful%20emissions%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESandeep%20Tiwari%2C%20founder%20of%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies%2C%20calls%20the%20Gold%20Composter%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmarvel%20of%20waste%20management%20technology%E2%80%9D.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20innovation%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20We%20have%20the%20expertise%20and%20versatility%20to%20design%20and%20implement%20large%20composters%20that%20can%20process%20hundreds%20of%20tons%20of%20organic%20waste%20in%20a%20single%20day%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandeep%20Tiwari%2C%20CEO%20of%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330329%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESandeep%20Tiwari%2C%20CEO%20of%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Does%20It%20Work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tiwari%2C%20the%20Gold%20Composter%20is%20an%20advanced%20aerobic%20organic%20waste%20composter%20which%20%E2%80%9Cemploys%20a%20completely%20natural%20bio-mechanical%20process%2C%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20our%20proprietary%20bacteria%20and%20bioreactor%20technology%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20breaks%20down%20organic%20waste%20rapidly%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20excessive%20heating%20and%20ensuring%20that%20no%20harmful%20emissions%20like%20methane%20are%20released%20into%20the%20environment.%20This%20results%20in%20a%20composting%20process%20with%20a%20low%20carbon%20footprint.%20Operating%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20aerobic%20decomposition%2C%20this%20cutting-edge%20technology%20employs%20oxygen-consuming%20microorganisms%20and%20bio-reactor%20to%20accelerate%20the%20breakdown%20of%20organic%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20machine%20facilitates%20aerobic%20composting%20by%20meticulously%20maintaining%20the%20ideal%20temperature%2C%20air%2C%20oxygen%2C%20and%20moisture%20conditions%2C%20guaranteeing%20a%20fast%20and%20efficient%20transformation%20of%20organic%20waste.%20Our%20organic%20waste%20composter%20output%20requires%20no%20further%20processing.%20It%20can%20be%20directly%20placed%20into%20aerated%20crates%20for%20storage%2C%20ready%20for%20later%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20agricultural%20purposes%2C%20Tiwari%20recommends%20allowing%20the%20compost%20to%20fully%20mature%20for%20three%20to%20seven%20days%20after%20processing%2C%20ensuring%20it%20reaches%20its%20peak%20nutrient%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20for%20landscaping%20and%20gardening%20needs%2C%20the%20compost%20can%20be%20utilised%20on%20the%20same%20day%20it%E2%80%99s%20produced%2C%20providing%20an%20instant%20boost%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318062%2Fiit-bombay-scientist-dr-rajul-patkar-innovates-portable-soil-testing-device-for-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoil%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20composter%20can%20treat%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20organic%20waste%20types%20%E2%80%94%20including%20cooked%20food%20waste%2C%20organic%20wet%20waste%2C%20bones%2C%20meat%2C%20feathers%2C%20eggshells%2C%20vegetable%20waste%2C%20tender%20coconut%2C%20horticulture%20waste%2C%20grass%20clippings%2C%20tissue%20paper%2C%20STP%20sludge%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20waste%20to%20compost%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Solid%20Waste%20Management%20Policy%202016%20mandates%20that%20bulk%20waste%20generators%20take%20responsibility%20for%20processing%20their%20waste%20right%20at%20their%20own%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20complements%20this%20policy%20seamlessly.%20By%20deploying%20our%20aerobic%20composter%20directly%20at%20our%20client%E2%80%99s%20premises%2C%20we%20empower%20bulk%20waste%20generators%20to%20comply%20with%20government%20directives.%20This%20not%20only%20eases%20the%20burden%20on%20landfills%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20We%20stand%20as%20reliable%20partners%20for%20communities%2C%20organisations%2C%20urban%20local%20bodies%20and%20institutions%20in%20their%20journey%20towards%20responsible%20waste%20management%20practices%20and%20help%20them%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Tiwari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20feeding%20organic%20waste%20into%20their%20Gold%20Composter%2C%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20their%20process%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmeticulous%20resegregation%E2%80%9D%20of%20waste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20ensures%20that%20no%20inorganic%20materials%20are%20present%20in%20the%20waste%20stream%20before%20it%20undergoes%20processing%20in%20our%20composter.%20This%20meticulous%20sorting%20not%20only%20optimises%20the%20efficiency%20of%20our%20composting%20process%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20nutrient-rich%20compost%20produced.%C2%A0%20As%20stated%20earlier%2C%20this%20compost%20can%20be%20utilised%20for%20landscaping%20and%20it%20can%20also%20be%20sold%20to%20farmers%20for%20organic%20farming%20practices.%20By%20closing%20the%20loop%20on%20organic%20waste%2C%20we%20promote%20sustainable%20waste%20management%20and%20foster%20a%20more%20eco-conscious%20and%20economically%20viable%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20claim%20holds%20some%20water%20given%20that%20their%20waste%20composter%20was%20purchased%20by%20the%20Central%20Food%20Technological%20Research%20Institute%20for%20research%20and%20development%20and%20to%20set%20composting%20standards%20across%20India.%20Thus%20far%2C%20their%20composters%20have%20been%20installed%20across%20approximately%20150%20locations%20around%20the%20country%20processing%20about%202%2C500%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20and%20generating%201%2C200%20tonnes%20of%20compost%20per%20month.%20But%20none%20of%20these%20developments%20happened%20overnight.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20around%20five%20years%20of%20extensive%20research%20and%20development%20before%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies%20arrived%20at%20its%20flagship%20Gold%20Composter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20journey%20began%20in%202014%20marked%20by%20a%20spirit%20of%20experimentation%20and%20innovation.%20By%202015%2C%20we%20had%20successfully%20developed%20our%20first%20prototype%2C%20a%20pivotal%20milestone%20that%20spurred%20us%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20research%20and%20development%20to%20refine%20our%20product%20further.%20Our%20first%20prototype%20transformed%20waste%20into%20compost%20in%2015%20days%20without%20the%20need%20for%20any%20time-consuming%20curing%20process.%20This%20achievement%20set%20us%20apart%20from%20our%20competitors.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20they%20typically%20required%20a%20protracted%2030%20to%2045%20days%20to%20achieve%20the%20same%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Tiwari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202018%2C%20his%20venture%20took%20the%20next%20significant%20step%20by%20incorporating%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20developed%20around%2010%20prototypes%20before%20arriving%20at%20our%20Gold%20Composter.%20Later%20that%20year%2C%20we%20introduced%20the%20Gold%20Composter%20to%20the%20market.%20Still%20awaiting%20a%20patent%2C%20the%20Gold%20Composter%20ranks%20among%20the%20fastest%20organic%20waste%20processors%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Feature-Image-1695133631.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gold%20composter%20which%20turns%20wet%20waste%20into%20compost%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Feature-Image-1695133631.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Feature-Image-1695133631-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Feature-Image-1695133631-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Feature-Image-1695133631-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-Feature-Image-1695133631-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330330%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3