d%20end%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%2017-year%20Santosh%20Trophy%20title%20drought%2C%20was%20equally%20fascinating.%20Sathyan%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20India%20squad%20that%20cantered%20to%20a%20gold-medal%20finish%20at%20the%201995%20SAF%20Games%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJo%20Paul%20Ancheri%20who%20played%20under%20Sathyan%E2%80%99s%20captaincy%20shared%20his%20dynamic.%20The%20former%20was%20widely%20regarded%20for%20his%20ability%20to%20play%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20positions%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20defensive%20midfielder%2C%20midfielder%2C%20and%20striker.%20His%20stellar%20performances%20during%20the%201993%E2%80%931994%20season%20established%20him%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20players%20in%20the%20country.%20Shortly%20after%20the%20season%2C%20he%20got%20a%20call%20to%20play%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIM%20Vijayan%E2%80%99s%20rise%20from%20poverty%20to%20stardom%20is%20a%20story%20for%20the%20books.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20he%20sold%20eatables%20in%20the%20Thrissur%20Corporation%20stadium%2C%20ironically%2C%20the%20same%20place%20that%20shaped%20his%20passion%20for%20the%20game%20and%20his%20career%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVijayan%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20football%20was%20spotted%20by%20Mr%20M%20K%20Joseph%2C%20the%20former%20DGP%20of%20Kerala%2C%20who%20took%20to%20the%20boy%20and%20adopted%20him%20into%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20former%20started%20his%20club%20career%20in%201989.%20The%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318215%2Fdelhi-boxer-rohit-tokas-won-bronze-medal-commonwealth-games-2022-despite-knee-injuries%2F%5C%22%20targ