Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20patient%20admitted%20in%20a%20different%20hospital.%20He%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F258900%2Fcoronavirus-origin-professor-padmanabhan-balaram-dorothy-hamre-unsung-woman-scientist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esevere%20pneumonia%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20fever%20and%20cough%20for%20three%20days%20along%20with%20a%20low%20platelet%20count%20and%20died%20of%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20in%20the%20emergency%20room.%20Although%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hail%20from%20the%20same%20village%20as%20the%20index%20case%2C%20the%20doctors%20were%20alert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20would%20a%20healthy%2C%20young%20adult%20die%20of%20pneumonia%20in%20just%20three%20days%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20unusual%20in%20the%20case%20of%20normal%20bronchopneumonia.%20We%20started%20probing%20in%20detail.%20We%20followed%20the%20Nipah%20protocols%20in%20handling%20the%20body%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20it%20to%20the%20family.%C2%A0We%20sent%20his%20sample%20also%20to%20NIV%20the%20same%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20there%20was%20an%20overlap%20between%20this%20patient%20and%20the%20first%20patient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20relative%20who%20was%20being%20treated%20in%20the%20same%20hospital%20as%20the%20index%20case.%20We%20got%20the%20discharge%20summary%20of%20that%20patient%20to%20establish%20the%20exact%20connection.%20He%20had%20been%20in%20the%20same%20ICU%20as%20the%20first%20patient%20who%20died%20on%2029%20August%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20critical%20care%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2042-year-old%20man%20and%20two%20of%20the%20four%20admitted%20tested%20positive%20for%20Nipah%20virus.%20Three%20others%20have%20also%20tested%20positive%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20Nipah%20cases%20currently%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%