%20encephalitis%20(inflammation%20of%20the%20brain).%20On%20evaluation%2C%20we%20found%20that%20his%20brother%20had%20died%20two%20weeks%20back%20with%20unusual%20symptoms.%20So%20the%20same%20three%20conditions%2C%20clustering%20of%20cases%2C%20unusual%20clinical%20symptoms%2C%20and%20contact%20with%20an%20index%20case%20gave%20us%20suspicion%20of%20a%20rare%20virus.%20Some%20symptoms%20mimicked%20Nipah%20and%20we%20sent%20the%20sample%20to%20Manipal%20virology%20institute%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20patients%20also%20lived%20near%20Janaki%20forest%2C%20home%20to%20many%20bat%20species.%20Fruit%20bats%20in%20a%20forest%20area%20here%20had%20tested%20positive%20for%20Nipah%20in%202018.%20Coincidentally%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%20hails%20from%20Ulliyeri%20village%2C%20which%20is%20just%2020%20kms%20from%20Janaki%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nipah%20outbreaks%20in%202018%2C%202019%20and%202021%20all%20presented%20with%20encephalitis%20symptoms.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20the%20symptoms%20are%20flu-like%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20diagnosis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20symptoms%20mimic%20flu%2C%20along%20with%20some%20central%20nervous%20system%20symptoms%20like%20confusion%2C%20convulsions%2C%20seizures.%20This%20time%20the%20presentation%20is%20very%20different.%20This%20is%20the%20season%20when%20influenza%20and%20pneumonia%20cases%20are%20a%20lot.%20We%20have%20to%20look%20carefully%20at%20family%20history%20and%20blood%20work.%20Most%20of%20these%20patients%20have%20low%20platelet%20count%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kumar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doctor%20was%20part%20of%20the%20medical%20teams%20in%202018%20and%202023%20who%20first%20diagnosed%20the%20virus%2C%20and%20helped%20in%20even%20faster%20discovery%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20in%202018%2C%20it%20took%2036%20hours%20for%20diagnosis%2C%20while%20this%20time%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20diagnose%20in%20just%2012%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%